        <div n="2" type="textpart">
          <head xml:lang="eng">Face</head>
          <p><lb n="1"></lb>dravya <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> <lb n="2"></lb>na vo ta tem svā<gap quantity="6" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> <lb n="3"></lb>nle moy neḥh cuṅ thnval man teṅ <gap quantity="11" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> <lb n="4"></lb>tapura mān kvān mvāy jmaḥ teṅ kr̥ṣṇa mān soca <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> <lb n="5"></lb>pre sarvāṅga ta kaṁsteṅ śrījayasiṅhavarmma nivedana <gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> <lb n="6"></lb>jvan rot ta vraḥ kala leṅ Āc mok pamre ta kamrateṅ Añ <supplied reason="lost">pa</supplied><lb break="no" n="7"></lb>nlas vraḥ śarira teṅ bhava <gap quantity="1" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> teṅ kr̥ṣ teṅ rudrāṇī teṅ <lb n="8"></lb>ke ni teṅ <gap quantity="1" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> te so teṅ sa<supplied reason="lost">ra</supplied>svatī syaṅ ta dār vraḥ ka<lb break="no" n="9"></lb>ruṇā prasā<supplied reason="lost">da</supplied> <gap quantity="6" reason="lost" unit="character"></gap> ta pamre ta kamrateṅ Añ <g type="unknown">.</g></p>
        </div>
